{"tid":2417423,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中国囚犯5毛獎勵標準曝光","createTime":"2021-02-22T00:56:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-22T12:16:43.000Z","uid":184679,"like":55,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"07e2b4ede145c5f12e75c3ce6a939225065c6889","tid":2417423,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T00:56:48.000Z","msg":"中國及海外社交平台遍佈中共網軍的言論，近日傳出，中國各地監獄竟在積極培訓囚犯成為網軍，並推行囚犯獎分標準，消息引發輿論譁然。<br />\n<br />\n2月17日，中國網易新聞刊出&lt;每個服刑人員都在努力地攢分&gt;的相關文章，有疑似知情網友在下方留言，透露了部分中國監獄給囚犯網軍的獎分標準：「發帖3分，跟貼1分，10萬分減（刑）半年。」<br />\n<br />\n該獎勵標準類似一般網軍「發帖5毛」的物質獎勵，因此引發民間關注。隨後，有網友在推特發文稱，「老少粉紅是不是要反省一下自己的智商，你們被一群『爭取自由』的囚犯給騙了」。<br />\n<br />\n也有網友計算，如果囚犯想要減刑半年，只需「跟帖」10萬或「發帖」3萬左右，由此感嘆想減刑的囚犯會替中國製造多少垃圾網文。另有網友感嘆，「發一帖需要30秒的話（登陸賬號、搜索話題、複製粘貼、截圖反饋）大概需要將近300個小時的工作可以減刑半年。難怪他們這麼用力。」<br />\n<br />\n上述消息尚未得到官方證實，但若消息屬實，囚犯網軍「產出」的貼文會比一般網軍速度快很多，因為囚犯一般生活比較簡單，除吃飯和睡覺外，可全天候「工作」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img3.secretchina.com/pic/2021/2-22/p2882151a887725290-ss.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg3.secretchina.com%2Fpic%2F2021%2F2-22%2Fp2882151a887725290-ss.jpg&h=dc579558&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國監獄網軍獎勵標準曝光後，海外多個中文媒體給予報導，不過，截止發稿前，網易新聞已將相關報導移除，原因不明。<br />\n<br />\n對此，有網友表示，「其實早就發覺那些跟貼的粉紅是囚犯了。活躍在貼吧和早期天涯論壇，文化極低，出口成『臟』，而且追著你亂咬。但凡正常點的人不會幹這種事。有點社會經驗的人，稍微動下腦子，就能猜出這就是囚犯。<br />\n<br />\n也有網友調侃道，「以後對五毛的問候語第一句是『你從哪間監獄出來的?』」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.secretchina.com/news/b5/2021/02/22/963308.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.secretchina.com%2Fnews%2Fb5%2F2021%2F02%2F22%2F963308.html&d=nAM79WGQOJ1S2Ssbv1FDYzKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=069db6a7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.secretchina.com/news/b5/2021/02/22/963308.html</a>"},{"pid":"82a744bee1dbd0848eebe10db97eb78d599a7200","tid":2417423,"uid":151074,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T01:03:22.000Z","msg":"如果全部五毛都捉曬入去坐，發文速度將會是現在的十倍以上<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"573efad74965380d99a8ff5c1ae14de847a983bf","tid":2417423,"uid":227628,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T01:04:47.000Z","msg":"誠懇問候各位五毛：你從哪間監獄出來的?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76b2f31d96691a0fc2c66d771238f66224207463","tid":2417423,"uid":33874,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T01:12:20.000Z","msg":"由五毛到三毛到一毛<br />\n而家變埋刑期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8ba33efe71e19471a065225dad965509516beb6","tid":2417423,"uid":235853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76b2f31d96691a0fc2c66d771238f66224207463","tid":2417423,"uid":33874,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T01:12:20.000Z","msg":"由五毛到三毛到一毛<br />\n而家變埋刑期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T01:18:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ff01449fa849f4d011f44e54edcb2e18793fb28","tid":2417423,"uid":49329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T01:19:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d105eb2fb0965c694d1f9875da4cb9c6c6f69f6","tid":2417423,"uid":279981,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"76b2f31d96691a0fc2c66d771238f66224207463","tid":2417423,"uid":33874,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"